# Bootstrap Parser — Recursive Descent Parser for Bootstrap Simple Subset
#
# Parses tokens from the bootstrap lexer into an AST stored in the arena
# from ast.spl. Handles:
#   - Function declarations (fn, extern fn)
#   - Struct declarations
#   - Variable declarations (val, var) at module and statement level
#   - Use/export declarations
#   - Expressions: arithmetic, comparison, logical, calls, indexing, field access
#   - Statements: assignment, return, if/elif/else, for..in, while, match/case, break, continue
#   - Indentation-based blocks
#
# Design: All state in module-level vars. Functions modify state.
# Works when compiled to C; not functional in interpreter (closure bug).

